| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2523 — Recovery Inhibition (raworld)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8d9b1476-5dc7-5bf6-b6ab-c532b2acf75d"
